          <div class="bks-photo-guide__rule"><span class="bks-photo-guide__icon">◻</span><strong>Neutral background</strong><span>White, beige or light grey wall. No doors, frames or clutter behind you.</span></div>
          <div class="bks-photo-guide__rule"><span class="bks-photo-guide__icon">◑</span><strong>Front light</strong><span>Window or natural light facing you. Avoid backlighting and harsh shadows on the face.</span></div>
